| Change [Balance](file:///Users/rajkushwaha/Desktop/develop/dotnet-projects/web_app_Csharp/web_app_Csharp/Models/Account.cs#32-37) from field → property `{ get; set; }` | C# Conventions |
| Create DTOs — don't expose DB models to API responses | DTO Pattern |
| Move learning comments → `NOTES.md`, clean production code | Clean Code |

