## Phase 3 — Complete Test Coverage

> "Do you write tests?" — the #1 interview question.

| Test Type | What to Test | Tools |
|---|---|---|
| **Unit Tests** (10+) | Deposit, Withdraw, edge cases, RetirementAccount bonus | xUnit + FluentAssertions |
| **Controller Tests** | Mock `DbContext`, verify HTTP status codes | Moq |
| **Integration Tests** | Real API endpoints with in-memory DB | WebApplicationFactory |

**Target: 15+ tests** covering happy paths, error paths, and edge cases.

```csharp
// FluentAssertions — reads like English
account.Balance.Should().Be(1500m);
result.Should().BeOfType<NotFoundResult>();
```

