## Modern C# to Use Throughout

```csharp
// Records — immutable DTOs (C# 9+)
public record AccountResponse(int Id, string Owner, decimal Balance);

// Primary Constructors — cleaner DI (C# 12+)
public class BankController(BankContext context) : ControllerBase { }

// Pattern Matching — elegant checks (C# 8+)
return account switch
{
    null => NotFound(),
    { Balance: < 0 } => BadRequest("Negative balance"),
    _ => Ok(account)
};

// Nullable Reference Types (C# 8+)
public string? EmailAddress { get; set; }
```

